---
// Hero section component - 重构版本，移除所有可能导致问题的SVG
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-secondary-50 py-20 sm:py-32">
  <!-- Background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-200 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 translate-y-1/2 w-80 h-80 bg-secondary-200 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <!-- Badge - 使用纯文本，移除SVG -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
        AI驱动的创业想法管理
      </div>

      <!-- Main heading -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        <span class="block">系统化管理您的</span>
        <span class="block text-gradient">创业想法</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Description -->
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        集成Gemini AI增强和Paul Graham评估框架的现代化创业想法管理平台。
        从想法记录到可行性评估，让每个创意都得到系统化的分析和管理。
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons - 使用CSS伪元素替代SVG图标 -->
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-primary btn-lg group">
          立即开始
          <span class="ml-2 inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn-secondary btn-lg group">
          了解更多
          <span class="ml-2 inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-y-1">↓</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">AI增强</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">智能分析和建议</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">PG框架</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">系统化评估方法</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">可视化</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">直观的数据展示</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator - 使用CSS伪元素替代SVG -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-400 text-lg">
      ↓
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
